ada-got-funk/article25787174.ece |website=The Hindu |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en-IN |date=20 December 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[K.G.F: Chapter 2]]''\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.filmibeat.com/kannada/news/2019/kgf-chapter-2-vijay-kirangdur-announces-the-release-date-january-2020-here-when-the-shoot-begins-281114.html|title= KGF Chapter 2 : Vijay Kirangdur Announces The Release Date! Here's When The Shoot Begins|author=Chaitra Krishnamurthy|date=3 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.xappie.com/entertainment-view/kgf-chapter-2-release-date-14538|title=KGF Chapter 2 release date!|author=Xappie Desk|date=2 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''[[Uttarayana (TV serial)|Uttarayana]]''\n| \n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Kumar S. |first1=Nanda |title=He spells success |url=https://www.deccanherald.com/content/312568/he-spells-success.html |website=Deccan Herald |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en |date=16 February 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''Nanda Gokula''\n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=S. M. |first1=Shashiprasad |title=Rad takes stork joyfully |url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/sandalwood/010818/rad-takes-stork-joyfully.html |website=Deccan Chronicle |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en |date=1 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004 \n| ''[[Silli Lalli]]'' \n|\n|\n| \n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Shiva'' (Dooradarshan)\n|\n|\n| \n|-\n|2006\n| ''Preethi Illada Mele'' \n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Kudige V. |first1=Samatha |title=A dream come true |url=https://www.deccanherald.com/content/66470/a-dream-come-true.html |website=Deccan Herald |accessdate=3 January 2019 |language=en |date=28 April 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''Male Billu''\n| \n|\n| \n|-\n| 2007\n| ''Sa''\n| \n|\n| \n|}\n\n== Music video appearances ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders unsortable\" style=\"text-align: margin;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 18em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 4em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 8em;\"| Composer\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 10em;\"| Director\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 8em;\"| Role\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 20em;\"| Notes\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 2em;\" | {{tooltip|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Spirit of Chennai]]\"\n| 2016\n| C. Girinandh\n| [[Vikram (actor)|Vikram]]\n| Himself\n| {{Non-album single}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-features/tp-metroplus/celebrating-the-spirit-of-chennai/article8083351.ece | title=Celebrating the spirit of Chennai | publisher=[[The Hindu]] | date=9 January 2016 | accessdate=22 March 2016 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322103414/http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-features/tp-metroplus/celebrating-the-spirit-of-chennai/article8083351.ece | archivedate=22 March 2016 | url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year{{efn|name=years|Refers to the year in which the award ceremony was held.}} !! Film !! Award !! Category !! Result !! Ref\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Moggina Manasu]]'' || [[Filmfare Awards South]] || [[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Kannada|Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Kannada]] || {{won}}|| <ref>{{cite web|title=56th Idea Filmfare Awards 2008 South: The winners|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/others/news-interviews/56th-Idea-Filmfare-Awards-2008-South-The-winners/articleshow/4845030.cms|accessdate=5 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Drama (2012 film)|Drama]]'' ||[[Filmfare Awards South]]||[[Filmfare Award for Best Actor \u2013 Kannada|Best Actor \u2013 Kannada]] || {{nom}}|| <ref>{{cite web|title=60th Idea Filmfa