anth Neel]]\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |last1=R. |first1=Shilpa Sebastian |title=Kannada got funk |url=https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/movies/kannada-got-funk/article25787174.ece |website=The Hindu |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en-IN |date=20 December 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[K.G.F: Chapter 2]]''\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.filmibeat.com/kannada/news/2019/kgf-chapter-2-vijay-kirangdur-announces-the-release-date-january-2020-here-when-the-shoot-begins-281114.html|title= KGF Chapter 2 : Vijay Kirangdur Announces The Release Date! Here's When The Shoot Begins|author=Chaitra Krishnamurthy|date=3 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.xappie.com/entertainment-view/kgf-chapter-2-release-date-14538|title=KGF Chapter 2 release date!|author=Xappie Desk|date=2 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''[[Uttarayana (TV serial)|Uttarayana]]''\n| \n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Kumar S. |first1=Nanda |title=He spells success |url=https://www.deccanherald.com/content/312568/he-spells-success.html |website=Deccan Herald |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en |date=16 February 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''Nanda Gokula''\n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=S. M. |first1=Shashiprasad |title=Rad takes stork joyfully |url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/sandalwood/010818/rad-takes-stork-joyfully.html |website=Deccan Chronicle |accessdate=28 December 2018 |language=en |date=1 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004 \n| ''[[Silli Lalli]]'' \n|\n|\n| \n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Shiva'' (Dooradarshan)\n|\n|\n| \n|-\n|2006\n| ''Preethi Illada Mele'' \n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Kudige V. |first1=Samatha |title=A dream come true |url=