 (2012 film)|Drama]]'' ||[[Filmfare Awards South]]||[[Filmfare Award for Best Actor \u2013 Kannada|Best Actor \u2013 Kannada]] || {{nom}}|| <ref>{{cite web|title=60th Idea Filmfare Awards 2013 (South) Nominations|url=http://www.filmfare.com/features/60th-idea-filmfare-awards-2013-south-nominations-3603-1.html|work=Filmfare|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707072232/https://www.filmfare.com/features/60th-idea-filmfare-awards-2013-south-nominations-3603-1.html|archivedate=7 July 2013|accessdate=5 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan='2'|2014|| [[Googly (film)|Googly]]'' ||[[Filmfare Awards South]]|| Best Actor \u2013 Kannada || {{nominated}}|| <ref>{{cite web|title=61st Idea Filmfare Awards (South) Nomination list|url=http://www.filmfare.com/features/61st-idea-filmfare-awards-south-nomination-list-6638.html|work=Filmfare|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001213159/https://www.filmfare.com/features/61st-idea-filmfare-awards-south-nomination-list-6638.html|archivedate=8 July 2014|accessdate=5 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Googly (film)|Googly]]'' || [[South Indian International Movie Awards|SIIMA]] || Best Actor \u2013 Kannada || {{nom}}|| <ref>{{cite news|title=SIIMA Awards 2014: Nominees and winners List for Kannada Movies|url=http://emptypage.in/siima-awards-2014-nominees-winners-list-kannada-movies/|accessdate=5 January 2015|work=The Indian Express|date=5 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2015 || rowspan=\"4\" | ''[[Mr. and Mrs. Ramachari]]'' ||[[Filmfare Awards South]]||Best Actor \u2013 Kannada || {{won}}|| <ref>{{cite web|title=Yash, Shwetha Srivatsav are Filmfare best actors|url=http://www.bangaloremirror.com/entertainment/south-masala/Yash-Shwetha-Srivatsav-are-Filmfare-best-actors/articleshow/47834933.cms|accessdate=27 June 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Filmfare Awards South]]|| Best Male Playback Singer - Kannada \"Annthamma\" || {{Nom}} ||\n|-\n|[[SIIMA]]|| Best Actor \u2013 Kannada || {{won}}|| <ref>{{cite news|title=Kannada award winners at S