ey.vice.com/en_us/article/7xyex4/the-100-best-albums-of-2018|title=Noisey's 100 Best Albums of 2018|work=[[Noisey]]|date=December 4, 2018|accessdate=December 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206102350/https://noisey.vice.com/en_us/article/7xyex4/the-100-best-albums-of-2018|archive-date=December 6, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[NPR Music]]\n| The 50 Best Albums of 2018\n| {{center|35}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2018/12/04/671206637/the-50-best-albums-of-2018-page-2|title=The 50 Best Albums of 2018|publisher=[[NPR Music]]|accessdate=December 4, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204142648/https://www.npr.org/2018/12/04/671206637/the-50-best-albums-of-2018-page-2|archive-date=December 4, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Okayplayer]]\n| The Best Albums of 2018\n| {{center|4}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.okayplayer.com/music/what-were-the-best-albums-of-2018.html|title=The Best Albums of 2018|publisher=[[Okayplayer]]|date=December 21, 2018|accessdate=December 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221121315/https://www.okayplayer.com/music/what-were-the-best-albums-of-2018.html|archive-date=December 21, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]''\n| The 50 Best Albums of 2018\n| {{center|23}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/the-50-best-albums-of-2018/?page=3|title=The 50 Best Albums of 2018|work=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|date=December 11, 2018|accessdate=December 11, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211131624/https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/the-50-best-albums-of-2018/?page=3|archive-date=December 11, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Rolling Stone]]''\n| 50 Best Albums of 2018\n| {{center|6}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-lists/50-best-